                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">The support from my teachers helped me align my passion with purpose and find clarity. Their guidance was instrumental in my journey to a top-tier art school, where I have thrived.<br><br>Foundation: London College of Fashion<br>Bachelor of Arts: Ravensbourne University<br>Master of Arts: Royal College of Art<br>Current Occupation: Creative Director (Fashion, Textiles & Fine Art)</p>
