                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">The diverse environment of West Island School shaped my global outlook. My journey from the United Nations (UN) to language education was inspired by the strength of the school’s programmes and pathways.<br><br>Career Footprint: Mali, Sweden, Brazil, Canada, the USA <br>Concordia University, Montreal<br>Bachelor of Commerce; Graduate Certificate in Business Administration<br>Bachelor of Education: Specialisation in TESL</p>
